Tom, I found that a little heat on the steel works.. see if you can get it 
to glow red.... then tap it with a center punch and hammer.. the crusty 
stuff around the steel that holds it inthe alum will disintigrate,, and the 
small plug of steel will fall out,
hope that helps
Jamie Rivers 

